attributes.Long form description: The student is preparing to play their Nintendo Switch. They insert the controllers into the handheld mode, then remove them and insert them into the Switch itself. They attach the straps to the controllers, open the kickstand, and exchange a game card. They remove the old Micro SD card and insert a new one, then turn on the Switch. Finally, they turn it off and put it on the table.
